I am using this code below to run out auto but our drive train doesn’t want to run any help I would greatly appreciate

return cantop.startSpeakerCommand()
.andThen(new WaitCommand(2.0))
.andThen(() → drivetrain.arcadeDrive(-.5, 0), drivetrain)
.withTimeout(8)
.andThen(() → drivetrain.arcadeDrive(0, 0), drivetrain);

andThen(Runnable) notation generates an instant command which runs the function just once.

You can use andThen(new RunCommand(() → drivetrain.arcadeDrive(-.5, 0), drivetrain)) to call the function continuously.

Edit: Also make sure that startSpeakerCommand has an end condition that actually ends.
